N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5204.3 - Time frame for submission of plans

State Regulations

The board shall administratively establish and publicize a
time frame for submission of plans, which shall be subsequent to its adoption
of this Part. Notes
